---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout darkContent={true} title="n8n 微信公众号博客发布工作流开发复盘" description="通过 n8n 工作流将个人网站博客内容自动发布到微信公众号草稿箱，完整记录踩坑过程与解决方案">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <time class="text-white/40 text-sm">2026-04-06</time>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-400 rounded text-xs">n8n</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded text-xs">微信公众号</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 rounded text-xs">工作流</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">n8n 微信公众号博客发布工作流开发复盘</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/60 mt-4">
        从零构建自动化工作流，将个人网站博客一键发布到微信公众号草稿箱
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="mb-12 p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-sky-400 mb-4">核心要点速览</h2>
      <details class="group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-white/60 hover:text-white text-sm">[ 点击展开思维导图 ]</summary>
        <div class="mt-6 overflow-x-auto">
          <!-- Miro-Style Mind Map -->
          <style>
            .mm-container { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; }
            .mm-center {
              background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
              color: white;
              padding: 16px 24px;
              border-radius: 12px;
              text-align: center;
              box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
              position: relative;
            }
            .mm-center-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.3; }
            .mm-center-sub { font-size: 11px; opacity: 0.8; margin-top: 4px; }
            .mm-branch {
              position: relative;
              padding-left: 24px;
              border-left: 2px solid;
            }
            .mm-branch::before {
              content: '';
              position: absolute;
              left: -2px;
              top: 20px;
              width: 16px;
              height: 2px;
            }
            .mm-node {
              background: white;
              border-radius: 8px;
              padding: 10px 14px;
              margin-bottom: 8px;
              position: relative;
              box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            }
            .mm-node::before {
              content: '';
              position: absolute;
              left: -20px;
              top: 50%;
              width: 16px;
              height: 2px;
              transform: translateY(-50%);
            }
            .mm-node-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; }
            .mm-node-sub { font-size: 11px; opacity: 0.7; margin-top: 2px; }
            .mm-challenge {
              background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
              border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
            }
            .mm-challenge .mm-node-title { color: #92400e; }
            .mm-challenge .mm-node-sub { color: #a16207; }
            .mm-solution {
              background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d1fae5 0%, #a7f3d0 100%);
              border-left: 3px solid #10b981;
            }
            .mm-solution .mm-node-title { color: #065f46; }
            .mm-solution .mm-node-sub { color: #047857; }
            .mm-flow { border-color: #3b82f6; }
            .mm-flow::before { background: #3b82f6; }
            .mm-flow .mm-node::before { background: #3b82f6; }
            .mm-config { border-color: #8b5cf6; }
            .mm-config::before { background: #8b5cf6; }
            .mm-config .mm-node::before { background: #8b5cf6; }
            .mm-grid {
              display: grid;
              grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
              gap: 16px;
              margin-top: 16px;
            }
            .mm-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
            .mm-connector {
              display: flex;
              align-items: center;
              gap: 8px;
              margin: 12px 0;
              color: #94a3b8;
              font-size: 12px;
            }
            .mm-connector::after {
              content: '';
              flex: 1;
              height: 1px;
              background: linear-gradient(90deg, #64748b, transparent);
            }
          </style>
          <div class="mm-container">
            <!-- Central Node -->
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="mm-center" style="min-width: 200px;">
                <div class="mm-center-title">n8n 微信公众号<br>博客发布工作流</div>
                <div class="mm-center-sub">自动化 · 零手动 · 草稿箱直达</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Flow Branches -->
            <div class="mm-connector">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/></svg>
              四大核心节点
            </div>
            <div class="mm-grid">
              <div class="mm-col">
                <div class="mm-branch mm-flow">
                  <div class="mm-node">
                    <div class="mm-node-title" style="color:#1e40af;">① 抓取博客 HTML</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">HTTP GET · 源站文章页面</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mm-branch mm-flow">
                  <div class="mm-node">
                    <div class="mm-node-title" style="color:#1e40af;">② 获取 access_token</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">微信 API · client_credential</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mm-col">
                <div class="mm-branch mm-flow">
                  <div class="mm-node">
                    <div class="mm-node-title" style="color:#1e40af;">③ HTML 样式转换</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">Tailwind → 内联样式 · 内容清洗</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mm-branch mm-flow">
                  <div class="mm-node">
                    <div class="mm-node-title" style="color:#1e40af;">④ 创建草稿箱</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">POST API · media_id 封面关联</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Challenges -->
            <div class="mm-connector">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 9v4M12 17h.01M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 001.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 001.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 00-3.42 0z"/></svg>
              三大核心挑战 → 解决方案
            </div>
            <div class="mm-grid">
              <div class="mm-col">
                <div class="mm-branch" style="border-color: #f59e0b; padding-left: 24px;">
                  <div class="mm-node mm-challenge">
                    <div class="mm-node-title">HTML 标签限制</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">微信公众号不支持 class/style 标签</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mm-node mm-solution" style="margin-top: 8px;">
                    <div class="mm-node-title">✓ Tailwind 转内联样式</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">replace class → style 属性</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mm-branch" style="border-color: #f59e0b; padding-left: 24px; margin-top: 12px;">
                  <div class="mm-node mm-challenge">
                    <div class="mm-node-title">access_token 传递</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">URL 参数被表达式覆盖问题</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mm-node mm-solution" style="margin-top: 8px;">
                    <div class="mm-node-title">✓ sendQuery + queryParameters</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">独立 query 参数传递 token</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mm-col">
                <div class="mm-branch" style="border-color: #f59e0b; padding-left: 24px;">
                  <div class="mm-node mm-challenge">
                    <div class="mm-node-title">内容边界提取</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">嵌套 div 正则匹配提前终止</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mm-node mm-solution" style="margin-top: 8px;">
                    <div class="mm-node-title">✓ indexOf/lastIndexOf</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub">精确位置计算替代正则</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mm-branch mm-config" style="margin-top: 12px;">
                  <div class="mm-node" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ede9fe 0%, #ddd6fe 100%); border-left: 3px solid #8b5cf6;">
                    <div class="mm-node-title" style="color:#5b21b6;">关键配置参数</div>
                    <div class="mm-node-sub" style="font-size:10px; line-height:1.6;">
                      AppID: wx964591c526715c17<br>
                      API: api.weixin.qq.com<br>
                      sendQuery: true<br>
                      thumb_media_id: 永久素材ID
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12">背景</h2>
      <p>
        个人网站使用 Astro + Tailwind CSS 构建，发布的博客文章采用 Tailwind class 样式。
        需要将这些博客文章自动化发布到微信公众号草稿箱，供后续编辑发布。
      </p>
      <p>
        微信公众号只支持有限的 HTML 子集，不支持：
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-white/60">
        <li>所有 <code>class</code> 属性（Tailwind 的核心）</li>
        <li><code>div</code>, <code>section</code>, <code>article</code> 等容器标签</li>
        <li>外部 CSS 和 <code>style</code> 属性（部分支持）</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12">工作流设计</h2>

      <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto">
        <pre class="text-green-400">Manual Trigger
      |
      v
+---------------+
| Fetch Article |  HTTP GET 抓取博客 HTML
+---------------+
      |
      v
+---------------+
| Get Token     |  获取 access_token
+---------------+
      |
      v
+---------------+
| Convert HTML  |  核心：HTML 清洗 + 样式转换
| Build Request |
+---------------+
      |
      v
+---------------+
| Create Draft  |  HTTP POST 到草稿箱 API
+---------------+</pre>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12">挑战一：微信公众号 HTML 限制</h2>
      <p>微信公众号支持的 HTML 核心标签非常有限：</p>
      <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <p class="font-semibold text-sky-400 mb-2">支持的标签</p>
        <p class="text-sm">
          <code>p</code>, <code>br</code>, <code>span</code>, <code>strong</code>, <code>em</code>,
          <code>u</code>, <code>h1</code>-<code>h4</code>, <code>ul</code>, <code>ol</code>,
          <code>li</code>, <code>blockquote</code>, <code>pre</code>, <code>code</code>, <code>img</code>
        </p>
      </div>
      <p>
        Tailwind 输出的 HTML 如 <code>&lt;h1 class="text-2xl font-bold"&gt;</code> 会全部失效，变成无样式纯文本。
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">解决方案：内联样式转换</h3>
      <p>在 Code 节点中使用 JavaScript 将 Tailwind class 转换为内联样式：</p>

      <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">
        <pre class="text-sm text-white/80">// 示例：Tailwind 转内联样式
articleHtml = articleHtml
  // 移除 class 属性
  .replace(/\s*class="[^"]*"/gi, '')

  // 转换代码块样式
  .replace(/&lt;code&gt;/gi, '&lt;code style="background:f4f4f4;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;"&gt;')

  // 转换标题样式
  .replace(/&lt;h2[^&gt;]*&gt;/gi, '&lt;p style="font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;margin:28px 0 14px;"&gt;')
  .replace(/&lt;\/h2&gt;/gi, '&lt;/p&gt;')

  // 转换段落样式
  .replace(/&lt;p([^&gt;]*)&gt;/gi, function(m, attrs) &#123;
    if (attrs.includes('style=')) return m;
    return '&lt;p style="margin:14px 0;line-height:1.9;"&gt;';
  &#125;);</pre>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12">挑战二：access_token 传递问题</h2>
      <p>
        这是踩坑最多的地方。微信公众号 API 要求 <code>access_token</code> 作为查询参数传递，
        但 n8n HTTP Request 节点的表达式处理有特殊规则。
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">错误方式</h3>
      <div class="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <pre class="text-sm text-red-300">// 错误：access_token 放在 URL 中
url: "https://api.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/draft/add?access_token=&#123;&#123; $json.access_token &#125;&#125;"

// 错误：sendQuery 配合 bodyParameters</pre>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">正确方式</h3>
      <div class="bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <pre class="text-sm text-green-300">// 正确配置
&#123;
  method: "POST",
  url: "https://api.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/draft/add",
  sendQuery: true,
  queryParameters: &#123;
    parameters: [&#123;
      name: "access_token",
      value: "=&#123;&#123; $json.access_token &#125;&#125;"
    &#125;]
  &#125;,
  sendBody: true,
  specifyBody: "string",
  contentType: "raw",
  rawContentType: "application/json",
  body: "=&#123;&#123; $json.body &#125;&#125;"
&#125;</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/30 p-4 rounded-lg mt-4">
        <p class="text-yellow-300 text-sm font-semibold">关键发现</p>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">
          <code>sendQuery: true</code> 时，URL 中不应包含已有的 query string，
          token 必须通过 <code>queryParameters</code> 单独传递。
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12">挑战三：文章内容边界提取</h2>
      <p>
        博客文章 HTML 中包含导航栏、侧边栏、footer 等非文章内容。
        最初使用正则表达式匹配 <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> 边界，但遇到嵌套标签时容易匹配错误。
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">错误方式</h3>
      <div class="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <pre class="text-sm text-red-300">// 错误：正则匹配遇到嵌套 div 会提前终止
const proseMatch = html.match(/class="prose"[\s\S]*?<\/div>/);
// 导致 content 字段只包含标题，内容被截断</pre>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">正确方式：精确位置计算</h3>
      <div class="bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <pre class="text-sm text-green-300">// 正确：使用 indexOf/lastIndexOf 精确计算边界
const articleStart = html.indexOf('&lt;article');
const articleEnd = html.lastIndexOf('&lt;/article&gt;');

// 找到 prose 类的开始位置
const proseClassIndex = html.indexOf('class="prose', articleStart);
const proseOpenTagEnd = html.indexOf('&gt;', proseClassIndex) + 1;

// 找到 footer 的开始位置（在 prose 区域内）
const footerStartInArticle = html.indexOf('&lt;footer', proseClassIndex);

// 提取两者之间的内容
const proseContent = html.substring(proseOpenTagEnd, footerStartInArticle);</pre>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12">完整工作流配置</h2>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-6">节点 1：Fetch Article from Website</h3>
      <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <tbody class="text-white/60">
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40 w-32">Method</td><td>GET</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40">URL</td><td><code>https://lysander.bond/blog/claude-code-wechat-integration</code></td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40">Response</td><td>text</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-6">节点 2：Get WeChat Access Token</h3>
      <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <tbody class="text-white/60">
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40 w-32">Method</td><td>GET</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40">URL</td><td><code>https://api.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/token?grant_type=client_credential&amp;appid=wx964591c526715c17&amp;secret=你的AppSecret</code></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-6">节点 3：Convert HTML &amp; Build Request</h3>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">这是核心节点，负责 HTML 清洗和请求体构建。</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-6">节点 4：Create WeChat Draft</h3>
      <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <tbody class="text-white/60">
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40 w-32">Method</td><td>POST</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40">URL</td><td><code>https://api.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/draft/add</code></td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40">sendQuery</td><td>true</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40">queryParameters</td><td>access_token = expression</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40">sendBody</td><td>true</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-1 text-white/40">contentType</td><td>raw (application/json)</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12">微信公众号适配版思维导图</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">微信公众号不支持 class、gradient、box-shadow，以下是纯文本适配版，可直接复制粘贴到微信编辑器：</p>

      <details class="mt-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-white/60 hover:text-white text-sm">[ 点击展开微信版思维导图 ]</summary>
        <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">
          <div style="font-family: Georgia, serif; line-height: 2; white-space: pre-wrap;">═══════════════════════════════════
     ◆  n8n 微信公众号博客发布工作流  ◆
       自动化 · 零手动 · 草稿箱直达
═══════════════════════════════════

  ▼ 四大核心节点

    ① 抓取博客 HTML
       └─ HTTP GET → 源站文章页面

    ② 获取 access_token
       └─ 微信 API → client_credential

    ③ HTML 样式转换
       └─ Tailwind → 内联样式 · 内容清洗

    ④ 创建草稿箱
       └─ POST API → media_id 封面关联

───────────────────────────────────

  ★ 三大核心挑战 → 解决方案

    ⚡ 挑战一：HTML 标签限制
       问题：微信公众号不支持 class/style 标签
       解决：Tailwind class → 内联 style 属性

    ⚡ 挑战二：access_token 传递
       问题：URL 参数被表达式覆盖
       解决：sendQuery + queryParameters 组合

    ⚡ 挑战三：内容边界提取
       问题：嵌套 div 正则匹配提前终止
       解决：indexOf/lastIndexOf 精确位置计算

───────────────────────────────────

  ⚙ 关键配置参数
     AppID:    wx964591c526715c17
     API:      api.weixin.qq.com
     sendQuery: true (必须)
     thumb_media_id: 永久素材ID</div>
        </div>
      </details>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12">踩坑总结</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-1">1. n8n sendQuery 模式</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70">使用 <code>sendQuery: true</code> 时，token 必须通过 <code>queryParameters</code> 传递，不能放在 URL 里。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-1">2. body 类型选择</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70">发送 JSON body 时，使用 <code>specifyBody: "string"</code> + <code>rawContentType: "application/json"</code>，而非 <code>jsonBody</code>。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-1">3. HTML 提取</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70">遇到嵌套标签时，位置计算（<code>indexOf</code>）比正则表达式更可靠。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
